<L>__{exterior castle hackton stables day}
<A>__{roderick, in a rage, taking a great horse whip, gallops off after the child.}
<L>__{exterior road castle hackton day}
<A>__{roderick comes upon a sad procession of farmers, moaning and howling, the black horse led by the hand, and, on a door that some of them carry, little patrick. he lies in his little boots and spurs, and his little coat of scarlet and gold. his face is quite white, and he smiles as he holds a hand out to roderick and says painfully:}
<C>__{patrick}
<D>__{you won't whip me, will you, papa?}
<A>__{roderick bursts out into tears in reply.}
